name: JPEG
description:
This is an illustration dedicated to amazing thread, started by 6529 on twitter that serves as NFT slang explanation for newcomers, as well as a collective item for those who know the way 

JPEG, JPG or JPGs

quote from @punk6529 aka 6529: "JPGs refers to our NFTs that might be JPGs or GIFs or PNGs or audio files or video files or computer games.

It is reclaiming a cope/insult for the community given many normies think "but you are just buying JPGs, are you mad?""
